{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"31cec79ffc","title":"毛泽东关于批林是批极左还是批右的谈话","origin":"原载王年一著《大动乱年代》，河南人民出版社，1988年，第451页。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3c20255028","index":0,"year":1972,"month":12,"day":17,"articleId":"31cec79ffc"}],"tags":[{"id":"18a89ee786","name":"王若水","type":"人物"},{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4716a370d2","type":"title","text":"关于批林是批极左还是批右的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"31cec79ffc"},{"id":"2cc85f1128","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"31cec79ffc"},{"id":"dc8a8a3391","type":"paragraph","text":"(一九七二年十二月十七日与张春桥、姚文元的谈话，游泳池)","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"31cec79ffc"},{"id":"24ddab4c81","type":"paragraph","text":"批极左，还是批右?有人写信给我，此人叫王若水。我认识此人，不很高明。也读过一点马克思，参加过合二而一、一分为二，桌子的哲学……","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"31cec79ffc"},{"id":"29663e57fa","type":"paragraph","text":"极左思潮少批一点吧。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"31cec79ffc"},{"id":"944e689a7c","type":"paragraph","text":"王若水那封信我看不对。 是极左? 是极右。修正主义，分裂，阴谋诡计，叛党叛国。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"31cec79ffc"},{"id":"6b5aa24e3b","type":"appellation","text":"（原载王年一著《大动乱年代》，河南人民出版社，1988年，第451页。）","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"31cec79ffc"}],"page":{"id":"1b28ce92ed","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"31cec79ffc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}